{
  "stem": "20142.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My hands were severely broken fingers and twisted out of proportion, as you can see.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They are not hands of arthritic condition.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were no medical attention taken during this period of time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I remember that the cold floor and wet floor of the cell helped me somehow to recover and to cope with it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--with time, it healed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was through the beatings of-- during the interrogation of the-- by the gestapo in Aleja Szucha in 1941.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By asking questions about certain activities, and certain people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] could not answer, and pleaded with them that I don't know them, don't know anything about it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they were beating me about the face, kicking me in groin, and stepping on my fingers while I was laying on the floor, and pulling it from under-- the hands from under their boots.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's how my finger was broken.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was not a simple situation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I somehow look at my fingers today and say, these are not arthritic fingers, they are strong hands.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But nevertheless, they are absolutely out of form.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'm grateful that I didn't lose any of them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When it comes to the life in the prison, there was quite simple.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [BACKROUND NOISE] It was routine conducting daily life by being waken up by a bell, and a sort of-- sort of very short wash up, and distribution of a little food.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then outside duties of cleaning the yards, or marching, or conducting some orders.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there were also people who were working in a tailor shop and in mechanical shops.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There were quite old prisoners staying in prison over a year, and they were privileged with these jobs.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
